<section id="fitur" class="relative py-24 px-[5%] lg:px-[8%] batik-bg" style="background-color: var(--cream);">
    <div class="relative z-10">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 text-[0.72rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] mb-3.5" style="color: var(--mango-green);">
            <span class="block w-8 h-[2px]" style="background: var(--gold);"></span>
            Fitur Unggulan
        </div>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); color: var(--leaf-dark); max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 16px;">
            Teknologi Cerdas <span style="color: var(--gold);">untuk Petani</span> Indramayu
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed max-w-[540px] mb-16" style="color: var(--text-light);">
            Menggabungkan kecerdasan buatan dengan kearifan lokal petani mangga Indramayu untuk hasil panen terbaik.
        </p>

        <!-- Features Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-7">
            <!-- Feature 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#D4A017]/20 relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(212,160,23,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--mango-green));"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5 border" style="background: var(--gold-pale); border-color: rgba(212,160,23,0.25);">🔍</div>
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--leaf-dark); margin-bottom: 10px;">Deteksi Kualitas Otomatis</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-light);">Unggah foto mangga dan sistem kami akan langsung menganalisis tingkat kesegaran, warna, tekstur, dan potensi cacat dalam hitungan detik menggunakan Computer Vision.</p>
                <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full" style="color: var(--mango-green); background: rgba(74,124,63,0.1);">CV AI</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#D4A017]/20 relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(212,160,23,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--mango-green));"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5 border" style="background: var(--gold-pale); border-color: rgba(212,160,23,0.25);">📊</div>
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--leaf-dark); margin-bottom: 10px;">Analitik Big Data Panen</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-light);">Pantau tren kualitas panen secara historis, prediksi waktu panen optimal, dan bandingkan performa kebun Anda dengan rata-rata petani Indramayu.</p>
                <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full" style="color: var(--mango-green); background: rgba(74,124,63,0.1);">Big Data</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#D4A017]/20 relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(212,160,23,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--mango-green));"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5 border" style="background: var(--gold-pale); border-color: rgba(212,160,23,0.25);">🥭</div>
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--leaf-dark); margin-bottom: 10px;">Database Varietas Lokal</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-light);">Didukung dengan data spesifik varietas mangga khas Indramayu: Gedong Gincu, Harum Manis, Cengkir, dan Manalagi dengan standar grading masing-masing.</p>
                <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full" style="color: var(--mango-green); background: rgba(74,124,63,0.1);">Lokal</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 4 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#D4A017]/20 relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(212,160,23,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--mango-green));"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5 border" style="background: var(--gold-pale); border-color: rgba(212,160,23,0.25);">📱</div>
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--leaf-dark); margin-bottom: 10px;">Antarmuka Mobile Friendly</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-light);">Dirancang untuk digunakan langsung di kebun. Antarmuka yang sederhana dan responsif memudahkan petani di mana saja tanpa perlu keahlian teknologi khusus.</p>
                <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full" style="color: var(--mango-green); background: rgba(74,124,63,0.1);">Mobile</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 5 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#D4A017]/20 relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(212,160,23,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--mango-green));"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5 border" style="background: var(--gold-pale); border-color: rgba(212,160,23,0.25);">🔔</div>
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--leaf-dark); margin-bottom: 10px;">Notifikasi Panen Cerdas</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-light);">Terima peringatan otomatis ketika mangga di kebun Anda siap dipanen berdasarkan analisis cuaca, musim, dan data historis panen sebelumnya.</p>
                <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full" style="color: var(--mango-green); background: rgba(74,124,63,0.1);">Smart Alert</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 6 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#D4A017]/20 relative overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(212,160,23,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 origin-left scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--mango-green));"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-[14px] flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-5 border" style="background: var(--gold-pale); border-color: rgba(212,160,23,0.25);">🤝</div>
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Lora', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--leaf-dark); margin-bottom: 10px;">Koneksi Pasar Digital</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-light);">Hubungkan langsung hasil panen berkualitas dengan pembeli, eksportir, dan pedagang besar melalui marketplace terintegrasi yang terpercaya.</p>
                <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full" style="color: var(--mango-green); background: rgba(74,124,63,0.1);">Marketplace</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
